# .graphifyignore — wick
# Block noise. Index Go source + curated docs.

# ── Build / vendor / cache ─────────────────────────────────────
vendor/
node_modules/
bin/
dist/
tmp/
logs/
.cache/
graphify-out/

# ── Editor / VCS / tooling ─────────────────────────────────────
.git/
.github/
.vscode/
.idea/
.claude/

# ── VitePress build output (keep docs/*.md sources) ────────────
docs/.vitepress/cache/
docs/.vitepress/dist/
docs/node_modules/
docs/public/
docs/**/image/

# ── Frontend build output / static assets ──────────────────────
web/public/
desktop/web/public/
desktop/bin/
**/static/

# ── Binaries & compiled artifacts ──────────────────────────────
*.exe
*.exe~
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib
*.test
*.out
gui.exe

# ── Lockfiles & manifests (low semantic signal) ────────────────
go.sum
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
*.lock

# ── DB / env / secrets ─────────────────────────────────────────
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# ── Media / fonts / binary assets ──────────────────────────────
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.svg
*.ico
*.webp
*.woff
*.woff2
*.ttf
*.eot
*.pdf
*.zip
*.tar.gz

# ── Generated / templates with low graph value ─────────────────
*.generated.go
*.pb.go
*_gen.go

# ── Heavy / low-signal docs ────────────────────────────────────
docs/changelog.md
LICENSE
